### Install Sanity Astro Integration with React

Source: https://github.com/sanity-io/sanity-astro/blob/main/README.md

Use `npx astro add` to install the `@sanity/astro` integration and `@astrojs/react` adapter. The React adapter is essential if you plan to embed a Sanity Studio within your Astro project.

```bash
npx astro add @sanity/astro @astrojs/react
```

